Module mesakit.map.measurements
Package com.telenav.mesakit.map.measurements.geographic

Class Area

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.map.measurements.geographic.Area
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Area>
public class Area extends Object implements Comparable<Area>
A square area on a Cartesian plane, measured as distance * distance. Areas can be created with the factory methods in this class or by calling Distance.squared() or Distance.by(Distance). Areas can be converted to different units, mathematically combined and compared with each other.
Author:
matthieun, jonathanl (shibo)
